org.forgerock.openam.sts.config.user

Class DeploymentConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.sts.config.user.DeploymentConfig
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SoapDeploymentConfig

    public class DeploymentConfig
extends Object
    This class represents the deployment configuration for an STS instance. This includes: 1. the AuthTargetMapping instance - i.e. the REST authN context for each token type. 2. The uri element at which the STS instance will be deployed 3. The realm within which the STS is deployed. For an explanation of what's going on with the builders in this class and its subclasses, see https://weblogs.java.net/blog/emcmanus/archive/2010/10/25/using-builder-pattern-subclasses
